        "Description": "Mister rabbit, how do you do ?\rMister rabbit, I took a habit from you\rMister rabbit, I made some friends \rMister rabbit, I left them dead\rMister rabbit, They were always true\rMister rabbit, the news shouldn&apos;t leak\rMister rabbit, you must not speak \rMister rabbit, remember I killed who \rMister rabbit, you&apos;re my friend too\r\r(Poem heavily inspired from &apos;Mr. Rabbit&apos; on hellopoetry.com)",
